label.DT_OD_TRADEIN_PROMPT_TITLE: Are you trading in a device?
label.DT_OD_TRADEIN_IPHONE_TURNOFF_TITLE: You need to turn off  'Find My iPhone' on your old device.
label.DT_OD_TRADEIN_IPHONE_TURNOFF_DESC: Instructions on how to turn off Find My iPhone will be in the trade-in box. If you don't turn it off, then your trade in value will be $0.

options.optionText: No, I won't be trading in a device.
